The article is a proclamation issued by President Donald Trump on January 21, 2020, regarding the sanctity of human life. The proclamation states that every person, including the unborn, has inherent value, and the rights of all people must be defended. It highlights the decrease in the number and rate of abortions in the country and the decrease in teen pregnancies. The President expresses his commitment to protecting the lives of the unborn and mentions legislation and regulations his administration has implemented to support this cause. He also mentions building an international coalition to oppose the concept of abortion as a fundamental human right. The proclamation calls on Congress to join in protecting and defending the dignity of every human life, and encourages the American people to support women in unexpected pregnancies, adoption, and foster care. The President concludes by urging citizens to raise their voices for all affected by abortion.